<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Dec1928"><font color="red">15 December 1928</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): We have got permission to leave here today much to our relief! &hellip; I can write this at last but all I can see to read is children&apos;s books with very large print. </div>
